name: Visit
description:
• 📇 Drag to create the directory structure and order you need.
  • 📃 Add '!' at the top of the page or frame name to ignore.
  • 📝 Click 'refresh' to update the changes in figma.
  • 👈 Hit 'reset' to initialize the list.</p>
  • 📠 Let others use the Visit plugin to share a view of the directory structure.
